</ul>
</section>
<section id="slide-org926e9b2">
<h4 id="org926e9b2"><span class="section-number-4">1.2.1</span> Formal Definition</h4>
<blockquote nil>
<p>
Computer programming is the process of designing and building an executable computer program to accomplish a specific computer result.
</p>
</blockquote>
