<section id="slide-orga1f48ef">
<h3 id="orga1f48ef"><span class="section-number-3">6.3</span> Um, why can't we just use <code>=</code> for equality</h3>
<p>
Like normal people&#x2026;
</p>
<ul>
<li class="fragment appear">Do we already have <code>=</code> in python?</li>
<li class="fragment appear">What does it do?</li>
<li class="fragment appear"><p>
Consider:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">

<pre><code class="python" >x = 1

x == 1
</code></pre>
</div></li>
<li class="fragment appear">Do we want them to be interchangeable?</li>

</ul>
</section>
